        "summary":  "Enterprise security AI adoption jumped from 50% to 78% year-over-year, but a SANS Institute survey finds 40% of practitioners report no formal AI adoption policies exist at their organizations. Over 60% of security teams lack visibility into where AI models are deployed, and a significant perception gap divides leaders (50% claiming formal risk programs) from frontline staff (only 36% confirming the same).",
